Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:09.77,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečítal som si ten list.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:15.64,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že Boris stále pokračuje v našom výskume na Islande.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:33.83,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Muselo sa mu stať niečo nezvyčajne, keď mi poslal lisť.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:40.64,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Len prečo ma kontaktoval teraz po desiatich rokov...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:53.65,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Pôjdem navštíviť svojho syna Andreia už čoskoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:31.75,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Epizoda 18.\NEkaterinburgsky mesiac
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:40.92,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepokúšaj sa na to ísť silou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:41.76,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.56,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak budeš isť na to silou, zlomí sa to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:50.50,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukľudni sa trochu a sprav to pomali, jemne a láskavo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:53.74,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Buď ticho, ja to viem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:57.64,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto to robím... Takto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.81,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď to chceš vyriešiť, musíš na to hľadieť, aký je to protivník.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:07.15,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Pri puzzle, musíš premýšlať ako to tvorca spravil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:11.12,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,O čom premýšlal? Ako rozložil to puzzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:13.82,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Akonáhle si to uvedomiš,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.69,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,budeš schopný to puzzle poskladať.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.20,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Rovnako to plati pre lásku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.47,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Volanie armády môže počkať.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.30,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Neni času sa najesť, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:30.14,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je Saya? Sú Saya a Riku v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:31.71,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Nič im nieje.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:35.18,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Práve su v meste Tyumen, ktoré je 300 Km východne odtiaľ to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:37.81,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Tyumen... Takže Tyumen, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:39.38,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde si sa vybral?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.32,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Pôjdem sa stretnúť so Sayaninou skupinou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:42.85,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,To neni nutné.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:46.62,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Pricestujú tu poobedňajším vlakom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.36,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Budu tu až zajtra ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.66,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Iste tak dlho nevydržíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.36,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Pôjdeš s nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.80,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, kto je ten 'Ted' mimochodom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.84,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Je vedeckým špecialistom v oblasti krvného výskumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:06.04,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Počas vojny vo Vietname bol prevedený do výskumného zariadenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:09.18,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,O niečo neskôr, on a paru jeho kolegov utieklo do Ruska.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:13.55,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Vo Vietname viedol vývoj Delty 67.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.75,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Delta 67...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.02,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Máš na mysli tú drogu čo zabila môjho odca?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:19.09,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.72,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže on je jeden s tých čo to vyrábal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.86,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,No, niesme si celkom istý.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:26.33,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz sa to budeme snažiť zistiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.27,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo tu zbran proste nevrátite?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:32.93,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz na to není čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:34.90,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Robíš si srandu? Je to zbraň môjho odca.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:39.71,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Poznáš význam tejto zbrane?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:57.93,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevyzera to, že je tam nejaké auto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:00.36,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Lewis, obídeme to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.90,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai, ti tu ostaň.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.57,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebuť blbý! Ja idem s vami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.10,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Zle si to pochopil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:10.54,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Bereme ta sebou, aby sme sa ujistili, že nespraviš nejakú blbosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:14.48,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ale, teraz potrebujeme niekoho, kto by nám postražil auto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:15.54,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Aby nás nezdržoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.62,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra bože!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.59,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Dostanem sa tam aj s Davidom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:51.95,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Lewis, všetko čisté.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.62,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to tak, že tu dneska ráno bol...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:14.77,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Musiš premýšla ako tvoj protivník.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:17.51,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Skús a uvidíš ako to urobil...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.87,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo do čerta to malo znamenať?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.31,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvádol som to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.19,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Hlavú hore, synku. Máme pre teba prácu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:36.56,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Dofrasa, najprv ste ma donutili riešiť puzzlový prstenec a teraz ma nútite robiť lupienkové puzzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:44.13,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Lewis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:46.40,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Je pekne stará...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:51.31,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Vzadu je napísané "27 November 1991".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.51,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,To bolo v čase zvrhnutia Sovietského režimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:59.81,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Atomová elekráren bola zaliata betonom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.49,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to podobné ako v Černobyľe, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.59,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,atomová elekráten celý ten incident zamaskovali?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:11.09,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to tam za partičku ľudi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:15.56,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty to nevieš? Ježiši, citim ako starí dedo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.37,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Černobyľsky atómový reaktor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:21.17,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,...sa v roku 1986 roztavil a explodoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:23.54,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Výbuch rozširil jedovatý popol cez celé Rusko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.07,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, budeme v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.44,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Na druhej strane, už si spravil čo si mal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:32.41,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,S ušetreným času! Čo, nie dokým mi nepodakuješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.75,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Poďakovať ti?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.95,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne potrebuješ poďakovanie za takú službu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.72,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak jedine čo chceš je vďaka, tak ti dám toľko koľko len budeš chcieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.73,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.63,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Tento list je adresovaný Filipovy Rosenbergovy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.87,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenbergovy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:55.64,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Je jedným z výskumníkov, ktorý utiekli z Vietnamu s Tedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:08:00.28,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Podľa naších správ, je pohrešovaný už desať rokov...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.88,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to také chaotické!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.61,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeš robiť svojú prácu trochu priehľadnejšiu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:08.22,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Sklapni. Urob si to sám, potom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.22,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Adresa je v priemyselnom parku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:13.32,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to neďaleko odtiaľto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:14.62,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Lewis...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:16.46,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ted tu možno stále je, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:21.06,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tam robiš? Pohni sa inak ťa tu necháme.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:23.43,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,P-počkaj chvíľu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:47.69,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Jak je na tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.53,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Žije, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:52.76,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Má slabý puls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:56.53,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,David!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:59.70,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Filip! Ste Filip Rosenberg, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.44,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Prišli sme sa vás opýtať ohľadom Teda. Kde je Ted?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.98,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je Ted A. Adams?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.28,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ted...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:15.48,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Správne. Kde je Ted A. Adams?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:17.82,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpovedz mi, Filip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:18.85,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Filip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.69,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, trochu s citom na starca.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.79,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč mi, Andrej...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:27.30,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Je mi to tak ľúto,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:30.03,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Andrej.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:31.33,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Andrej?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:34.14,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to moja chyba...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:37.17,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Čakáj na mňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.71,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Niekedy iste...  Mesiac...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.41,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukážem ti mesiac...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.88,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,To je strata času. Je kopletne senilni.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:51.42,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Filip, kde je Ted?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.99,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Sľúbil som.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:58.66,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Určite...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:00.53,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesiac...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.56,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesiac...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:08.50,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Je mrtvy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:09.57,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:11.57,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Iba zaspal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:21.12,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,To je ten sami obrazok, ktorý sme našli v Tedovej izbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:26.25,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten pravo v strede je Filip, predpokládam...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:29.72,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta stena...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:32.43,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Sverdlovsk-51!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.77,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Andrej...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:19.64,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďalšie anime na:\Nwww.youtube.com/zaxyss
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:22.48,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Andrej...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:01.55,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Není o tým pochyb.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.82,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to Tedové auto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:04.89,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Potom, Ted musí byť v nútri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:12.06,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže, to má byť ten speedo-box, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:15.23,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Sverdlovsk-51.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:19.80,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Za sovietského režimu to bolo ukrité mesto, ktoré sa  podieľalo na výrobe jadrovej zbrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:20.74,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.21,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Motor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.68,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to, že generátory stále fungujú.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.05,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Je v poriadku byť tu s tou radiáciou na okolo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.15,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Radiácia je len výmysel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.06,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Výmysel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:45.33,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Dáva ľudom dôvod držať sa odtiaľto ďalej.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:52.37,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, beží to na benzíne a nie na uránovom palive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:00.54,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Výťah je dole.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:01.71,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,To pôjdeme tam dole?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.21,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevadí ak tam nejdeš s nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.18,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Nič také som nepovedal! Ja idem tiež.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.92,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre prídad, tu asi hore ostanem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.45,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým chceš povedať?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:21.90,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,David!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.03,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai, ty zostaneš tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.07,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,V žiadnom prípade! Idem s vami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.94,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa do hodiny nevrátime,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:33.07,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,vráť sa do hotelu a nahlás to Júlii.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.91,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Až potom rob, čo uznáš za vhodné.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:13:36.08,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,V poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.08,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:45.29,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si prišiel do Ruska?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.49,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Sprav to, čo je tvoja primárna úloha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.73,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,My sme tí, ktorých záležitosť je tam dole.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.64,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Neobávaj sa, vrátime sa včas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:19.92,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Oci...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.28,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Lewis, našiel som bombu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:48.05,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak myslíš tú obednú krabičku, tak tu je dalšia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.50,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiropteran!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:06.40,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,To je ted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:09.97,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeš sa dostať s tej kocky?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:13.07,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem dnu. Rozptyľ ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:14.31,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:25.82,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu som! Chutím lepšie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.06,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Oy, je to bezpečné?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:37.73,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Vydržte!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.67,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ste Ted A. Adams, správne?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:42.44,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,David!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:02.36,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Lewis, padáme preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.12,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.44,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto ste?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.44,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Červený štít?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.78,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo chcete so mnou tak neskoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:26.98,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten Chiropteran...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.72,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Stvorili ste to monštrum?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.12,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to môj syn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:39.46,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Delta 67, ktorú som vzal z Vietnamu ho premenila na monštrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:42.06,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa stalo vo Vietname?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.00,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Robili sme krvný výskum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.84,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Oficiálne, pod rozkazmi z hora,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:52.24,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,vyvýjali sme rozširený samožijúci krvný transfúzny produkt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:56.75,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,V skutočnosti, traja z nás pracovali
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:17:02.32,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,na dlhodobo skladovanej jedinečnej krvnej skupine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.12,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedinečnej krvnej skupine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.26,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,To je on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:11.69,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Prichádza!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.63,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je Delta 67?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:18.83,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Delta 67 bola vyrobená s tej jedinečnej krvnej skupiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.81,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolo to tak prekrásne dievča...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.19,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,To je moja posledná otočka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.32,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte jeden!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.03,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,David...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:56.80,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sme prve dokončili Deltu 67,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:01.60,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol som predstavený darcovy tej jedinečnej krvnej skupine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.57,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Krvnemu darcovi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:07.21,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to tak prekrásna mladá dievčina...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:15.38,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Krásna a divoká, ale hrozbou celeho ľudstva...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:19.65,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Jej meno bolo Diva.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:28.00,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale všetko bolo zničene počas vianočneho bombardovania v roku 1972.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:31.67,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:36.00,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Umiestnil som boli po celej tejto budove.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:40.94,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Detonátor je v mojom aute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.08,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Môj syn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:46.01,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím pochovajte môjho syna...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:50.09,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepač mi to, Andrei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:33.06,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa stane tej Chiroptere?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:37.97,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravdepodobne bude spať...\Ncelú večnosť...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.37,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Pochovajme toho chlapa tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:45.04,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,David!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.81,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra, je to vážne poranenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:54.82,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa mu to stalo na chrbte?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:21:00.16,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Na bojisku čelil Chiroptere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:04.03,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoril, že ako jediny prežil z celej jeho čaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:09.20,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Odkedy prežil, nemal inú možnosť ako pokračovať v boji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:16.10,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to kríž, ktorý musí niesť.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:25.58,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Dostal si nádchu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:28.08,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, som v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:30.52,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak by ma zajimalo, či to nemaš od tej zimy z vonku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:33.52,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Požičal som si Hajiho kabát, tak mi bolo teplo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.12,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.06,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem, Haji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:39.73,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie tak celkom. Nepotrebujem vďaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:44.30,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Vy tiež, Liza, ďakujem, že ste nás s tamaď vytiahli.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:48.14,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Len vďaka vám sa všetci dostaneme do Ekaterinburgu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:49.47,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:52.37,Magic Purple,,0000,0000,0000,,Som rada, že môžem byť nápomocná.
